   "source": "## Part C½ — Push LoRA adapter to HuggingFace Hub\n\nUpload the trained adapter so it can be loaded by the HuggingFace Space (or any other deployment).\n\n### Setup (one-time)\n\n1. Create a free account at [huggingface.co](https://huggingface.co).\n2. Go to [Settings → Access Tokens](https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens) and create a **Write** token.\n3. In Colab, open the **Secrets** sidebar (🔑 icon) and add it as `HF_TOKEN`.\n\n### What this does\n\n- Pushes only the small LoRA adapter files (a few MB) to your HuggingFace account.\n- The base model (`google/gemma-2-2b-it`) is already public — only the adapter needs to be uploaded.",
