   "source": "## Part E — Interactive Web Interface (Gradio)\n\nLaunch a **Hebrew-RTL chat interface** to interact with the fine-tuned model.\n\n- Runs directly in Colab (or locally with a GPU).\n- Provides a shareable public link via Gradio's `share=True`.\n- Styled with a dark theme and RTL support for Hebrew text.",
